headline: Wall Street's Insights Into Key Metrics Ahead of Revvity (RVTY) Q2 Earnings
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Revvity (RVTY), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended June 2025.
